net.sf.uadetector.datastore
Class NotUpdateableXmlDataStore

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.uadetector.datastore.AbstractRefreshableDataStore
      net.sf.uadetector.datastore.NotUpdateableXmlDataStore
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataStore, RefreshableDataStore
public final class NotUpdateableXmlDataStore
extends AbstractRefreshableDataStore

This is a very simple implementation of a DataStore for test cases which want to update the UAS data with unreachable URLs.

Author:
André Rouél
